Source: kde3-kdiff3
Section: kde
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruud Koolen <ruudkoolen@ruudkoolen.nl>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), kde3-kdelibs4-dev, kde3-libkonq4-dev, libqt3-mt-dev, docbook-to-man, automake1.9, autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: kde3-kdiff3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: kde3-kdiff3-doc
Description: compares and merges 2 or 3 files or directories
 KDiff3 compares two or three input files and shows the differences
 line by line and character by character. It provides an automatic
 merge facility and an integrated editor for comfortable solving of
 merge conflicts. KDiff3 allows recursive directory comparison and
 merging as well.

Package: kde3-kdiff3-doc
Architecture: all
Recommends: kde3-kdiff3
Description: documentation for kdiff3
 KDiff3 compares two or three input files and shows the differences
 line by line and character by character. This package contains the 
 HTML documentation.

